 single\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1775}, {\"ngram\": \"a Dream\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1791}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1813}, {\"ngram\": \"Katerine\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1842}, {\"ngram\": \"the scene\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 1855}, {\"ngram\": \"so much criticism\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1892}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The opening ceremony did ruffle some feathers\\u2026 and I LOVE it.\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1957, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1916}, {\"ngram\": \"some feathers\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You know why?'\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 1972, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"she began.\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 1983, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Because theOlympicsare the biggest stage in the world and us queer people have always been the audience of other people's life and achievement and it is the time that were are welcome in the space.'\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 2184, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the biggest stage\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2026}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2039}, {\"ngram\": \"us queer people\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2059}, {\"ngram\": \"the audience\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2089}, {\"ngram\": \"other people's life\", \"from\": 2093, \"to\": 2112}, {\"ngram\": \"achievement\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2128}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2147}, {\"ngram\": \"the space\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nicky Doll performs her newest single, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098I had a dream\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099, at the Opening Ceremony of the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris, France.pic.twitter.com/LPKstCXW1P In an earlier post, Doll said it was an 'honour' to perform on the very biggest stage, putting 'queerness on the screen' of billions across the globe.\", \"from\": 2186, \